OL,3,CElectoral Authority reviewing
OL,4,Ccandidate's conduct after group email
OL,6,FJersey's Electoral Authority is
OL,7,Flooking into the conduct of St Saviour
OL,8,FConstable Kevin Lewis after he is
OL,9,Funderstood to have used parish
OL,10,Fcommunications to promote his re-
OL,11,Felection campaign.
OL,13,FThe States Greffe told ITV News the
OL,14,Fmatter is being reviewed and an update
OL,15,Fwill be issued if appropriate, as
OL,16,Fofficials consider whether he broke
OL,17,Felection law.
