OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776708665
OL,3,CElectoral Authority reviewing
OL,4,Ccandidate's conduct after group email
OL,6,FPeople took to social media after
OL,7,Freceiving the parish email newsletter
OL,8,Fearlier this week, which appears to be
OL,9,Fwritten by Constable Lewis, laying out
OL,10,Fhis achievements and re-election bid.
OL,12,FThere was also an article on the
OL,13,Fparish website promoting his campaign,
OL,14,Fwhich has since been removed.
OL,16,FAs chair of the committee which
OL,17,Foversees Constables, Mike Jackson says
OL,18,Fhe has received a letter from the
OL,19,FElectoral Authority raising its
OL,20,Fconcerns.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
