OL,3,CElectoral Authority reviewing
OL,4,Ccandidate's conduct after group email
OL,6,FHe adds: "Whilst individual
OL,7,FConnetables will run their election
OL,8,Fcampaigns as they wish, the Comite
OL,9,Fwould certainly not endorse using
OL,10,Fparish resources for private electoral
OL,11,Fpurposes."
